#. type: Plain text
#: NeoIPC-Core-Protocol.adoc:643
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Complete this field if signs of infection were identified during the "
"surgical procedure.  The signs of infection must be noted intraoperatively "
"and documented in the narrative part of the operation note or report of "
